properties.propertyVal:
SELECT
	SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_KEY AS ENROLLMENT_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.PROGRAM_INVITATION_ID AS PROGRAM_INVITATION_ID
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_ID AS ENROLLMENT_ID
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENTITY_KEY AS ENTITY_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.PROSPECT_KEY AS PROSPECT_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.PROGRAM_KEY AS PROGRAM_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.INVITATION_CODE AS INVITATION_CODE
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.INVITATION_EXPIRES_ON_DATE_KEY AS INVITATION_EXPIRES_ON_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.INVITATION_CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS INVITATION_CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.INVITATION_CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS INVITATION_CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.INVITATION_UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS INVITATION_UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.INVITATION_UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS INVITATION_UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.USER_KEY AS USER_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.PROXY_KEY AS PROXY_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.INSURANCE_POLICY_KEY AS INSURANCE_POLICY_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_KIND AS ENROLLMENT_KIND
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_CONFIRMED_AT_DATE_KEY AS ENROLLMENT_CONFIRMED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_CONFIRMED_AT_TIME_KEY AS ENROLLMENT_CONFIRMED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS ENROLLMENT_CREATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS ENROLLMENT_CREATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS ENROLLMENT_UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY AS ENROLLMENT_UPDATED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.HAS_ENROLLMENT AS HAS_ENROLLMENT
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.HAS_INVITE AS HAS_INVITE
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.DELETED_AT_DATE_KEY AS DELETED_AT_DATE_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.DELETED_AT_TIME_KEY AS DELETED_AT_TIME_KEY
	,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.IS_DELETED AS IS_DELETED
      
         , SRC_ods_dim_user.USER_ID AS USER_ID
         , SRC_ods_dim_program.PROGRAM_ID AS PROGRAM_ID
	 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MY_MYSQL_FACT_ENROLLMENT SRC_ods_fact_enrollment 
JOIN dim_user SRC_ods_dim_user ON SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.user_key = SRC_ods_dim_user.user_key
JOIN dim_program SRC_ods_dim_program ON SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.program_key = SRC_ods_dim_program.program_key
WHERE  
STR_TO_DATE(CAST(SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ENROLLMENT_UPDATED_AT_DATE_KEY AS CHAR(8)),'%Y%m%d')> DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL $SP_LOOK_BACK_DAYS.look_back_days DAY )

attributes.attrExprVal:
CASE 
	WHEN SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.enrollment_kind IS NULL OR SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.enrollment_kind  <> 'EligibleEnrollment'
        THEN    COALESCE(SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.V_ENROLLMENT_CONFIRMED_AT_DATE ,SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.V_ENROLLMENT_CREATED_AT_DATE )
	ELSE NULL
END

DI_CF
(
CASE 
	WHEN SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.enrollment_kind IS NULL OR SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.enrollment_kind  <> 'EligibleEnrollment' then 1
	ELSE 0
END 
)

dCmd_Inst.dCmd:
UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'ABORTED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING';

INSERT INTO control_load_history (data_flow_name, status, start_timestamp, created_at)
VALUES ('DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS', 'RUNNING', $$CurrentTimeStamp, $$CurrentTimeStamp);

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'FAILED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'SUCCEEDED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
SRC_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS.SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.SourceCount    , 
SRC_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS.SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.ProcessCount  , 
SRC_target_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS.SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.TargetCount  , 
SRC_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS.SRC_ods_fact_enrollment.BadCount  ,
TGT_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_eligibility.SourceCount   , 
TGT_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_eligibility.ProcessCount  , 
TGT_target_count  =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_eligibility.TargetCount   , 
TGT_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS.TGT_fact_eligibility.BadCount   ,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_fact_eligibility_V3_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'
